    <item>
      <title>押注大幅降息，债券市场涨势“变得危险”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/bond-rally-turns-dangerous-to-chase-with-bets-on-big-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期美联储将很快开始以对抗衰退的步伐降息，债券价格正在上涨，这带来交易员再次低估美国经济实力的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/bond-rally-turns-dangerous-to-chase-with-bets-on-big-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
